evidence.text: ORDER granting 9 Motion to Dismiss. This case is hereby dismissed without prejudice for lack of subject matter jurisdiction. The motion to stay discovery and objections to Magistrate Judge Joel C. Hoppe's Order thereon are Denied as Moot. The Clerk is hereby directed to strike this case from the active docket of this court. Signed by Judge Norman K. Moon on 3/13/17.
